  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a reaction when you take damage, you can entomb yourself in otherworldly matter, which fades away at the end of your next turn. You gain 5 temporary hit points per warlock level, which take as much of the triggering damage as possible. Immediately after you take the damage, your speed is reduced to 0, and you are incapacitated. These effects, including any remaining temporary hit points, all end when the matter fades away.</p><p>Starting at 5th level in warlock, the temporary hit points increases to 10 per warlock level.</p><p>Once you use this invocation, you cannot use it again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>",
